Name: Wedding Photography
description: widely published around the world and he is represented by some of the leading picture libraries. His work has featured in some of the leading projects on wildlife photography like Wild Wonders of Europe and 2020 Vision. In 2014 he had his first feature published in National Geographic which was on the iconic Atlantic Puffin. He co-owns Natures Images and he set this up with Mark Sisson in 2007 and together they have built it one Europe’s premier photo tour companies.
